data2017Q3$first.treat0708 = case_when(data2017Q3$Nearest0708_FWHTreatment == '2018-01-01' ~ 20180101,
          data2017Q3$Nearest0708_FWHTreatment == '2017-01-01' ~ 20170101,
          data2017Q3$Nearest0708_FWHTreatment == 'NT' ~ 0
          )

data2017Q3$first.treatHalfYear = case_when(data2017Q3$NearestHalfYear_FWHTreatment == '2018-07-01' ~ 20180701,
                                     data2017Q3$NearestHalfYear_FWHTreatment == '2017-07-01' ~ 20170701,
                                     data2017Q3$NearestHalfYear_FWHTreatment == '2016-07-01' ~ 20160701,
                                     data2017Q3$NearestHalfYear_FWHTreatment == '2015-07-01' ~ 20150701,
                                     data2017Q3$NearestHalfYear_FWHTreatment == 'NT' ~ 0
)

### Process tlist as numeric
data2017Q3$week_start_date_numeric = as.numeric(stringr::str_replace_all(data2017Q3$week_start_date,"-","")) 
data2017Q3$first.treat.start2017Q3_numeric = as.numeric(stringr::str_replace_all(data2017Q3$first.treat.start2017Q3,"-","")) 

data2017Q3$first.treat.start2017Q4_numeric = as.numeric(stringr::str_replace_all(data2017Q3$first.treat.start2017Q4,"-","")) 
### Run model 1
out.fect1 <- fect(normal_pickup_count~ TreatmentLabel_2017Q3 + NormalUserPostCount,
                  data = data2017Q3, index = c("creator_ward_key","week_start_date"),
                  method = "fe", force = "two-way",se = TRUE, seed = 1234)

data2017Q3$log_normal_pickup_count = log(data2017Q3$normal_pickup_count + 1)
data2017Q3$log_NormalUserPostCount = log(data2017Q3$NormalUserPostCount + 1)

### Run model 1 with log log ->
